  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajitham competition in the election of the new president",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa will also contest as a candidate during next week's vote for the new President in Parliament.",
        "During this, a special discussion was held on Friday 15th under the leadership of opposition party leader Sajith Premadasa about getting the support of other parties.",
        "At the same time, Tamil Progressive Alliance Vice President Velusami Radhakrishnan said that attention was paid to this resolution.",
        "In this discussion Sri Lanka Freedom Party General Secretary Dayasiri Jayasekara and its members Dumintha Dissanayake, Lasantha Ajayavanna, Ranjith Siyambalapitiya and others, Tamil Progressive Alliance Vice Presidents Velusami Radhakrishnan and Palani Digambaram, Left Democratic Front Leader Vasudeva Nanayakkara, Lanka Sama Samaj Party President Prof. Thissa Vidharana, Sri Lanka Labor Congress General Secretary Jeevan Thondaman, Tamil National Federation Speaker President's Attorney MA Sumanthran, Tamil People's National Alliance President CV Wickhineswaran were present.",
        "According to the general agreement, the meeting between the United People's Power, the United People's Alliance and the opposition parties was about creating an all-party program for building the country, and the meeting was held to create a program for a specific period of time through the common program for building the country.",
        "In this regard, Tamil Progressive Alliance Vice President Velusami Radhakrishnan told Kesari,",
        "Arrangements have been made for opposition leader Sajith Premadasa to contest next week's vote for the election of the new president. They are currently implementing the decision already taken in this regard. In this regard, it was discussed in this meeting to take steps to get the aspirations and support of other members. mentioned that."
      ],
